        <short-description type="string">Automated high-altitude cruise safety watchdog.</short-description>
        <long-description type="string">Copilot Pillow acts as an automated virtual copilot during steady, long-haul high-altitude cruise phases. It actively monitors your live AGL altitude alongside calibrated airspeed (for airplanes) or main rotor RPM (for helicopters). If you step away from the controls and the aircraft drops below your safe limits while remaining at cruise altitude, the add-on instantly triggers a pause state, preventing a catastrophic stall or crash.</long-description>

